doc:
Extracts a slice corresponding to the portion of the path remaining for iteration.

# Examples

```
use std::path::Path;

let mut components = Path::new("/tmp/foo/bar.txt").components();
components.next();
components.next();

assert_eq!(Path::new("foo/bar.txt"), components.as_path());
```
